 word and by teaching for doctrines the commandments </div><div class="t m6fd x71 h4 y2bb ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of men. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
